      "updated": 1774151158537,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "DIMENSIONS:\n    -dim_part (CAD)\n    -dim_assembly (PLM)\n    -dim_supplier (ERP)\n    -dim_revisions (PLM-SCD type 2)\n\nFACT TABLES:\n    -fact_bom (Assembly <->Pat Mapping)\n    -fact_cost (Part cost)\n    -fact_design (Design Attributes)\n\nOPTIMIZATION:\n    -Partitioning (date)\n    -Z-Ordering (part_id)",
      "fontSize": 31.321039932498014,
