      "updated": 1774151158537,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "+Metadata Layer: \" Pipeline memory\"\n    -Tracks Data\n    -Enables Debugging \n    -Ensures Governance \n\n\n• Watermark Table (ERP Incremental Tracking)\n• CDC Tracking Tables (PLM Change Tracking)\n• File Tracking Logs (CAD Batch Files)\n• Data Lineage (Source → Bronze → Gold)\n• Schema Evolution Tracking\n• Data Quality Metrics (Nulls, Duplicates)\n• Data Catalog (Purview / Glue)",
      "fontSize": 81.22208057691131,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "+Metadata Layer: \" Pipeline memory\"\n    -Tracks Data\n    -Enables Debugging \n    -Ensures Governance \n\n\n• Watermark Table (ERP Incremental Tracking)\n• CDC Tracking Tables (PLM Change Tracking)\n• File Tracking Logs (CAD Batch Files)\n• Data Lineage (Source → Bronze → Gold)\n• Schema Evolution Tracking\n• Data Quality Metrics (Nulls, Duplicates)\n• Data Catalog (Purview / Glue)",
