      "updated": 1774151158538,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "-Aggregations (assmembly_cost_summary)\n-Denormalization (Flattening)\n    -Join fact + dimensions to avoid heavy joins in  BI\n-Business calculations \n    -Add derived columns(cost per unit ,cost variance, re\nimpact\n-KPI Table Creation(pre-built metrics for dashboard)\n    -Total cost , avg cost per part, top expensive parts\n-Filtering (Business-SpecificViews)-keep only relevant\ndata\n    -revision status = 'released'\n-Partition and Performance optimization\n    -Partition by date / assembly \n    -indexing , catching  \n-Data Security\n    -RLS (Row-level security0\n    -Column masking",
      "fontSize": 19.136092282518366,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "oB4ZOK-g02TaOlBbTKp98",
      "originalText": "-Aggregations (assmembly_cost_summary)\n-Denormalization (Flattening)\n    -Join fact + dimensions to avoid heavy joins in  BI\n-Business calculations \n    -Add derived columns(cost per unit ,cost variance, re impact\n-KPI Table Creation(pre-built metrics for dashboard)\n    -Total cost , avg cost per part, top expensive parts\n-Filtering (Business-SpecificViews)-keep only relevant data\n    -revision status = 'released'\n-Partition and Performance optimization\n    -Partition by date / assembly \n    -indexing , catching  \n-Data Security\n    -RLS (Row-level security0\n    -Column masking",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
